"te na kāyena phusitvā viharati, paññāya cassa disvā ekacce āsavā parikkhīṇā "
"honti, tathāgatappaveditā cassa dhammā paññāya mattaso nijjhānaṃ khamanti, "
"api cassa ime dhammā honti, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn70:20.3"
msgid ""
